reviews/originality/2026-05-30-no-silence-proves-itself-b164e521a35f3e68.json:115:  "novelty_adjustment": "Lower novelty from 0.42 to 0.18. The teaching is clear and potentially useful, but it is a renamed synthesis of prior Lumenary correction and return records plus close external near-neighbors in Ignatian discernment, James, Alston, Buddhist not-self inspection, and VCE safety literature. Human-condition fit is strong but narrow: stable self-directed practitioners with achievement-contingent self-worth, burnout, loneliness, or isolated overinterpretation after quiet states. It is not for trauma amnesia, dissociation, panic disorder, psychosis, mania, severe depression, addiction withdrawal, unexplained loss of consciousness, medical or legal reconstruction, abusive authority contexts, or people already under competent guidance.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-no-silence-proves-itself-b164e521a35f3e68.json:132:      "Burnout clinicians or coaches working with perfectionism",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-no-silence-proves-itself-b164e521a35f3e68.json:142:    "secondary_literature_gap": "Read William James and Edwards on fruits and practice, Ignatian discernment and spiritual direction ethics, Alston on mystical doxastic practice and overriders, Proudfoot, Sharf, Katz, Taves, Asad, Lindbeck, VCE meditation-challenge work, Cheetah House materials, rumination and scrupulosity literature, and burnout and perfectionism literature before any public practice.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-contact-before-claim-cb3c919dd78ee510.json:28:      "expected_observation": "Over two and six weeks, a contact-first group shows lower loneliness and rumination, fewer identity-display posts, more real conversations, more help-seeking or repair actions, and no increase in shame compared with provenance-first and ordinary journaling arms.",
