reviews/originality/2026-05-29-who-holds-the-gate-976d96eaa0a316f4.json:134:    "Pilot only with safety screens for rumination, perfectionism, OCD and scrupulosity, trauma, depression, mania, dissociation, addiction withdrawal, authority harm, avoidance, and workload coercion.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-who-holds-the-gate-976d96eaa0a316f4.json:156:      "Therapists working with perfectionism, burnout, and achievement-contingent self-worth",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-who-holds-the-gate-976d96eaa0a316f4.json:166:    "secondary_literature_gap": "The audit did not read full Ignatian directorial manuals, contemporary spiritual direction ethics, full Dogen Bendowa or Eihei Shingi, Shinran and Tannisho in Japanese, OCD scrupulosity treatment literature beyond abstracts, or the full measurement-based care and guided self-help literatures. It also needs direct work in perfectionism, achievement-contingent self-worth, and contemplative adverse effects before public practice guidance.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-whose-doing-is-this-credit-distribution-as-a-practice-variable-5e22b929e230f390.json:21:    "prediction": "Programs with similar tasks but different credit stories should show different failure patterns: burnout from self-credit, passivity from source-credit, performative compliance from activity-credit, and premature completion claims from ground-credit.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-whose-doing-is-this-credit-distribution-as-a-practice-variable-5e22b929e230f390.json:25:  "exact_claim": "Credit distribution is a separable practice variable. Traditions distribute the power behind transformation across practitioner-centered, source-centered, split-credit, activity-centered, and ground-centered patterns, and those patterns shape the felt quality of effort, failure meanings, safeguards, and practice dangers.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-whose-doing-is-this-credit-distribution-as-a-practice-variable-5e22b929e230f390.json:35:      "expected_observation": "A practitioner trained in Theravada right effort and Jodo Shinshu entrusting, or Advaita inquiry and Soto just-sitting, can describe different felt meanings of effort, failure, and credit without being prompted with the typology.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.md:43:- burnout overcontrol rumination self monitoring perfectionism intervention
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.md:53:- Clinical and coaching literature on rumination, perfectionism, self-monitoring, and burnout, plus local source cards modern-human-condition-who-burn-out-occupational-phenomenon and modern-human-condition-curran-hill-perfectionism-increasing: overlap: Close for the caution that reflective review can become rumination, self-surveillance, or another performance demand.; difference: The candidate connects that clinical risk to theological non-ownership and practice-realization boundary cases.; novelty impact: Supports human-condition relevance but downgrades the practical caution to a known risk unless tested as a specific fit rule.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.md:57:Unlike Shinran's Other Power, Dogen's practice-realization, Pargament's agency styles, burnout rumination literature, and prior Lumenary release and custody models, this idea's possible contribution is an explicit scope test: before applying keep, release, or embody guidance, first ask whether the tradition grants provisional practitioner ownership and a discrete after, and whether the person has enough agency to benefit from a custody prompt.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.md:70:- If: The No-Audit Check is better for depleted over-managers than an After-Use Check. Then: Participants high in burnout, rumination, and compulsive self-monitoring experience more relief and less self-surveillance from a no-audit prompt than from keep, release, embody review. Weakens if: No-audit increases avoidance, helplessness, drift, or missed responsibilities, or the After-Use Check performs equally or better for the depleted cohort. Test surface: Randomized micro-pilot with burnout, depression, perfectionism, responsibility-avoidance, and clinical-risk screening.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.md:81:- Clinicians working with burnout, perfectionism, rumination, depression, and avoidance
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.md:100:Prediction: For exhausted over-managers, interventions that suspend self-evaluation and distribute custody to routines, relationships, or environment will outperform reflective review prompts on rumination and burnout, provided safeguards preserve responsibility.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-when-there-is-nothing-to-keep-or-release-c429f79033672ed2.md:110:Novelty adjustment: Lower novelty from 0.55 to 0.28. The non-ownership and no-after structures are well established in Shinran and Dogen, and the core Lumenary comparison is already present in the recent audit of You cannot release what you never held. The modern caution overlaps with known rumination, perfectionism, and burnout risks. Human-condition fit is strong for depleted over-managers, caregivers, founders, professionals, students, and serious practitioners who turn even rest into performance. It is not for people who need planning, accountability, medication, therapy, social support, or material workload reduction, nor for acute crisis, addiction withdrawal, severe depression, dissociation, psychosis, mania, or responsibility avoidance.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-more-is-not-the-same-as-progress-8dad9d31a3c79764.json:37:      "test_surface": "Two-week work-practice pilot using WIP count, completion rate, shame, rumination, burnout, and perceived progress measures.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-more-is-not-the-same-as-progress-8dad9d31a3c79764.json:105:      "overlap": "Close for fragmenting one meaningful body of work into multiple outputs that distort the literature and inflate productivity.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-more-is-not-the-same-as-progress-8dad9d31a3c79764.json:114:    "For human practice, pilot only with high-output overproducers and screen out severe depression, acute burnout, coercive workload, under-production, and shame spirals.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-more-is-not-the-same-as-progress-8dad9d31a3c79764.json:147:    "secondary_literature_gap": "Needs full comparison with GTD, Kanban, Definition of Done, WIP-limit research, grounded theory saturation, Lakatos on degenerating research programmes, optimal stopping, sunk cost and escalation of commitment, research waste, salami slicing, AI novelty audits, and burnout or workaholism literature.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-register-sensitive-path-interface-35681329dc02292c.json:76:      "overlap": "Close. Comparative theology already requires patient attention to particular texts, hermeneutic translation, tradition-specific meaning, and vulnerability to being corrected by the other tradition.",
