reviews/originality/2026-05-29-a-clock-measures-a-path-8cd5d80af738d5d8.md:110:Novelty adjustment: Lower novelty from 0.50 to 0.34. Human-condition fit is direct but already well-covered by social clock theory, chrononormativity, social acceleration, burnout, and perfectionism literature. Target cohort: functioning adults who meet obligations but feel late in life because of visible peer timelines. Non-fit cases: acute crisis, severe depression, mania, psychosis, addiction withdrawal, people avoiding duties, and people facing structural exploitation where schedule pressure is materially imposed rather than internal comparison.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-a-clock-measures-a-path-8cd5d80af738d5d8.md:118:- Interview physicists, social-clock researchers, burnout clinicians, caregivers, and team leads for concrete failure and repair cases.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-surplus-grain-test-3d2d262887cc1740.md:28:Structural observation: SN 45.8 presents path factors as trainable functions, including right view, right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion. Dogen's Bendowa makes zazen not merely one transferable technique but the expression of the Way itself, where practice and realization are not cleanly separated. The pair supports the candidate's distinction between repeated operation and practice grammar. Similar sitting or effort can have different meaning, authority, and endpoint structures.
