reviews/originality/2026-05-29-keep-what-can-correct-you-8144312cebdf1b38.md:50:- Talal Asad, The Idea of an Anthropology of Islam, https://bpb-ap-se2.wpmucdn.com/thinkspace.csu.edu.au/dist/c/3891/files/2020/10/Asad-Anthropology.pdf, and George Lindbeck, The Nature of Doctrine: overlap: Close theoretical prior. Practice meaning, correct form, purpose, authority, and doctrine as grammar are already tied to traditions and communities.; difference: The candidate narrows this to post-practice correction after unusual experience.; novelty impact: Downgrades broad originality. The possible contribution is an operational prompt, not a new theory of religious authority.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-keep-what-can-correct-you-8144312cebdf1b38.md:52:- Internal Lumenary prior, A practice cannot name itself, reviews/originality/2026-05-28-a-practice-cannot-name-itself-df9d5fed41c6e168.md: overlap: Very close internal prior. It already says a practice does not authorize the meaning of its own result and asks who or what can name the event.; difference: This candidate shifts from naming authority to correction after method release.; novelty impact: Internal novelty is reduced. Cross-index rather than publish as a standalone discovery.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-keep-what-can-correct-you-8144312cebdf1b38.md:107:Novelty adjustment: Lower novelty from 0.48 to 0.36. Human-condition fit is real but already strongly supported by loneliness, meaning-loss, perfectionism, burnout, spiritual-direction, and meditation-safety prior art. Target cohort: stable self-directed practitioners, app meditators, cross-tradition seekers, and retreatants without continuing guidance. Non-fit cases: acute crisis, psychosis, mania, dissociation, addiction withdrawal, severe depression, abusive communities, and practitioners already under competent teacher or clinical care.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-threshold-grammar-under-translation-strain-63091c8c41cd9e28.md:12:A tradition's account of how transformation begins should be treated as a threshold grammar under translation strain. The research unit is the paired record of how the tradition narrates entry, what that narration predicts about threshold safeguards and beginner warnings, and what meanings are lost when entry grammars are compared across traditions. The model becomes serious only if first-break type improves prediction after anthropology, authority, conversion process, ritual inheritance, and practice ecology are coded separately.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-threshold-grammar-under-translation-strain-63091c8c41cd9e28.md:17:- A first-break comparison must carry translation-strain fields: preserved meaning, bent meaning, dropped meaning, and false-convergence risk.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-threshold-grammar-under-translation-strain-63091c8c41cd9e28.md:102:- Where would comparing your entry grammar to grace, vow, stream-entry, recognition, or practice-realization bend or drop meanings you regard as decisive?
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-threshold-grammar-under-translation-strain-63091c8c41cd9e28.md:132:- Build a pre-registered split-source coding sheet with fields for entry grammar, threshold marker, preserve meaning, bent meaning, dropped meaning, false-convergence risk, anthropology, authority, conversion process, ritual inheritance, practice ecology, safeguard, beginner warning, evidence passage, and confidence.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-method-s-reckoning-what-a-practice-does-with-its-own-authority-at-completion-54774578d7528e56.json:52:    "Mystical Languages of Unsaying meaning event",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-method-s-reckoning-what-a-practice-does-with-its-own-authority-at-completion-54774578d7528e56.json:56:    "Zhuangzi fish trap words meaning forget words text"
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-first-ask-if-a-path-agrees-with-itself-67802a7a8e6bf629.json:129:  "novelty_adjustment": "Lower novelty from 0.60 to 0.52. The idea combines known internal-diversity critique, comparative-method selection theory, anti-essentialism, and statistical effect-size logic. The possible contribution is the explicit denominator gate for Lumenary translation-strain scoring. Human-condition fit is moderate: it serves reflective readers unsettled by digital comparison and meaning loss, but it is not a practice for acute distress or for people using analysis to avoid commitment.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-you-cannot-release-what-you-never-held-3f00413ce244b54e.md:20:- The modern human problem is achievement-contingent self-worth and burnout, not spiritual completion in general.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-you-cannot-release-what-you-never-held-3f00413ce244b54e.md:69:- If: Release teaching is cohort-specific medicine for active earning and result-ownership. Then: High-striving practitioners who describe results as earned will show reduced pride, shame, comparison, and burnout after the Earning Check, while other-power or practice-realization practitioners will show little benefit or increased self-monitoring from the same instruction. Weakens if: All cohorts benefit equally, or the instruction mainly licenses avoidance, passivity, or contempt for ordinary responsibility. Test surface: Randomized pilot stratified by self-power language, perfectionism, tradition background, and achievement-contingent self-worth.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-you-cannot-release-what-you-never-held-3f00413ce244b54e.md:81:- Clinicians and coaches working with perfectionism, burnout, and achievement-contingent self-worth
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-you-cannot-release-what-you-never-held-3f00413ce244b54e.md:99:Prediction: Coaches who screen for perceived result ownership before giving detachment advice will reduce perfectionistic rumination and burnout better than coaches who give universal 'let go of the outcome' advice.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-you-cannot-release-what-you-never-held-3f00413ce244b54e.md:109:Novelty adjustment: Lower novelty from 0.55 to 0.39. The strongest prior-art pressure is Lewin's middle-voice analysis plus Shinran's explicit Other Power and Pargament's agency styles. Human-condition fit is strong but narrow: high-striving people with achievement-contingent self-worth, burnout, comparison, and result-ownership. Non-fit cases include acute crisis, severe depression, addiction withdrawal, scrupulosity, dissociation, psychosis, people in grace-centered or nondual practice who do not experience ownership, and people whose distress is caused mainly by structural exploitation rather than self-rating.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-you-cannot-release-what-you-never-held-3f00413ce244b54e.md:117:- Run the Earning Check pilot only after screening for perfectionism, scrupulosity, avoidance, workload coercion, and clinical risk. Track whether it reduces self-worth conversion without weakening responsibility.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-the-self-was-never-a-conclusion-ebf3587c6da573ba.md:114:Novelty adjustment: Lower novelty from 0.58 to 0.29. The Advaita self-luminosity claim is well known, the Buddhist not-self strategy is well known, and the internal Lumenary dialogue from 2026-05-26 already made the decisive asymmetric correction to the inference-policy model. The FEP corollary overlaps with The Brain Model Already Took a Side and Formal Recurrence of the Inferential Gap. The human-condition fit is plausible but narrow: stable adults with anxious self-verdicts after quiet, blank, or absorbed states, especially where meaning loss and achievement-contingent self-worth are active. It should not be used for depersonalization or derealization disorder, OCD or scrupulosity checking, psychosis, mania, acute dissociation, severe depression, addiction withdrawal, trauma activation, or situations needing rest, food, human company, teacher guidance, or clinical care rather than inward attention.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-method-release-has-a-shape-fc7b25df89b750ea.json:42:      "test_surface": "Small randomized micro-pilot with measures for perfectionism, burnout, rumination, responsibility avoidance, and ordinary conduct.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-method-release-has-a-shape-fc7b25df89b750ea.json:57:    "WHO burnout occupational phenomenon Curran Hill perfectionism increasing"
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-method-release-has-a-shape-fc7b25df89b750ea.json:102:    "Pilot The After-Use Check only with screening for perfectionism, scrupulosity, avoidance, workload coercion, dissociation, mania, trauma activation, severe depression, and clinical distress."
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-method-release-has-a-shape-fc7b25df89b750ea.json:104:  "novelty_adjustment": "Lower novelty from 0.68 to 0.26. The core structure is already present in internal Lumenary records and in external raft, ladder, apophatic, therapeutic, and practice-realization sources. Human-condition fit is real but narrow: it serves achievement-contingent self-worth, perfectionism, burnout, and compulsive self-improvement among functioning practitioners. It is not a fit for acute crisis, addiction withdrawal, severe depression, dissociation, psychosis, mania, under-motivation, responsibility avoidance, or structural burnout where workload and material conditions are primary.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-method-release-has-a-shape-fc7b25df89b750ea.json:123:      "Clinicians or coaches working with perfectionism, burnout, and compulsive self-improvement"
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-you-cannot-prove-the-one-who-is-asking-6e5f448135e13ebe.md:110:Novelty adjustment: Lower novelty from 0.45 to 0.31. The question-admissibility move is a useful extension of prior Lumenary work, but it is close to Shankara scholarship, Fasching on prakasa, Mandukya commentary, and the already audited Brain Model and Inferential Gap records. Human-condition fit is plausible but narrow: achievement-contingent self-worth and compulsive self-justification in stable adults. It is not a general treatment for loneliness, depression, anxiety, dissociation, OCD, scrupulosity, trauma, addiction, or avoidance of responsibility.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-who-holds-the-gate-976d96eaa0a316f4.md:22:- The human-condition target is achievement-contingent self-worth, perfectionism, burnout, and spiritual or reflective avoidance.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-who-holds-the-gate-976d96eaa0a316f4.md:32:Secondary literature gap: The audit did not read full Ignatian directorial manuals, contemporary spiritual direction ethics, full Dogen Bendowa or Eihei Shingi, Shinran and Tannisho in Japanese, OCD scrupulosity treatment literature beyond abstracts, or the full measurement-based care and guided self-help literatures. It also needs direct work in perfectionism, achievement-contingent self-worth, and contemplative adverse effects before public practice guidance.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-who-holds-the-gate-976d96eaa0a316f4.md:49:- contingencies of self-worth Crocker Park achievement contingent self-worth perfectionism burnout
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-who-holds-the-gate-976d96eaa0a316f4.md:78:- If: Gate custody interacts with practitioner state. Then: In a screened pilot, bypass-state participants show improved ordinary conduct and reduced avoidance after a return check, while compulsive-scorer participants show more rumination and self-criticism after self-held checks than after fixed-rule, clinician-held, teacher-held, or resultless-practice alternatives. Weakens if: Self-held return checks help scorers as much as bypassers, or externally held and fixed-rule gates do not reduce rumination relative to self-held checks. Test surface: Randomized micro-pilot with measures for rumination, self-critical rumination, achievement-contingent self-worth, perfectionism, conduct follow-through, avoidance, burnout, and mood.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-who-holds-the-gate-976d96eaa0a316f4.md:79:- If: Oscillation is state-level and revisable, not a trait label. Then: Within-person diary or EMA data will show the same practitioner moving between bypassing and scoring states across contexts, and state-level routing will predict next-day outcomes better than a one-time trait classification. Weakens if: Trait labels predict outcomes as well as state-level data, or people classified as oscillators do not show meaningful within-person switching. Test surface: Two-week ecological momentary assessment with brief prompts after practice, work review, conflict, and rest periods.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-who-holds-the-gate-976d96eaa0a316f4.md:91:- Therapists working with perfectionism, burnout, and achievement-contingent self-worth
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-who-holds-the-gate-976d96eaa0a316f4.md:130:- Read full sources before public use: Ignatian directorial literature, contemporary spiritual direction ethics, VCE and Cheetah House materials, Pargament, measurement-based care, guided self-help, rumination and self-focused attention, achievement-contingent self-worth, perfectionism, spiritual bypassing, and scrupulosity ERP.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-who-holds-the-gate-976d96eaa0a316f4.md:132:- Pilot only with safety screens for rumination, perfectionism, OCD and scrupulosity, trauma, depression, mania, dissociation, addiction withdrawal, authority harm, avoidance, and workload coercion.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-claimant-strain-credit-diagnostics-d0a05f55d7f0bf18.md:12:Credit distribution should not function as a master taxonomy. First code the native claimant grammar, meaning what may count as agent, action, transformation, and causal attribution. Then score translation strain between traditions. Only after that should stage-level credit distribution be tested for added prediction of safeguards beyond claimant grammar, institution, teacher authority, initiation structure, and existing agency-allocation models. Low-strain cases may support taxonomy; high-strain cases should count as boundary cases or analogies, not confirming evidence.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-contact-before-claim-cb3c919dd78ee510.md:32:Risk of overread: High if published as a discovery. Conduct-testing, fruits-testing, counsel, disclosure, practice-realization, social connection, and anti-checking are all established. The idea can overread loneliness as a source-confusion problem, or underread appropriation, power, and unsafe community risk. Human-condition fit is clearer than many recent records but narrow: stable lonely or digitally unmoored seekers, people facing meaning loss, feeling out of place, digital comparison, and achievement-contingent spiritual identity. It is not for unsafe relationships, abusive groups, acute grief crisis, OCD or scrupulosity, dissociation, mania, psychosis, severe depression, addiction withdrawal, medical concern, coercive workload, or cases where a teacher, clinician, or safeguarding pathway should hold the next step.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-contact-before-claim-cb3c919dd78ee510.md:36:- Contact before claim borrowed spiritual sentence provenance contact conduct loneliness pastoral discernment
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-contact-before-claim-cb3c919dd78ee510.md:43:- Sherry Turkle Reclaiming Conversation Alone Together online performance connection loneliness
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-contact-before-claim-cb3c919dd78ee510.md:45:- social prescribing loneliness systematic review community connection behavioral activation
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-contact-before-claim-cb3c919dd78ee510.md:51:- Jonathan Z. Smith, In Comparison a Magic Dwells, https://classics.osu.edu/sites/classics.osu.edu/files/Magic_Dwells.pdf: overlap: Close on similarity, contiguity, borrowing, and the danger of projecting a scholar's perceived relation into an objective relation.; difference: The candidate turns comparison discipline into a routing protocol for public doctrine versus private loneliness.; novelty impact: The comparison-control core is known; the use-and-wound switch remains the possible contribution.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-contact-before-claim-cb3c919dd78ee510.md:55:- William James, The Varieties of Religious Experience, https://www.gutenberg.org/files/621/621-h/621-h.html: overlap: Strong near-neighbor for fruits over roots and practice as evidence. James already says origin alone cannot decide spiritual value and that fruits must be judged.; difference: James does not split public doctrine from private orientation, nor does he add appropriation and digital-loneliness safeguards.; novelty impact: Major downgrade for contact-and-conduct testing.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-contact-before-claim-cb3c919dd78ee510.md:61:- Liz Bucar on religious appropriation, University of Chicago Divinity School, https://divinity.uchicago.edu/sightings/articles/what-religious-appropriation-and-why-does-it-matter: overlap: Close anomaly pressure. Religious borrowing can be morally neutral or harmful depending on injustice, authority, and community meaning, not just user intention.; difference: The candidate says some private use may begin with contact, but Bucar shows why public or harmful use may need ethics and provenance first.; novelty impact: Lowers confidence unless the protocol has an upfront appropriation and safety screen.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-contact-before-claim-cb3c919dd78ee510.md:62:- Social connection and social prescribing evidence, HHS advisory https://www.hhs.gov/surgeongeneral/reports-and-publications/connection/index.html and systematic review https://ijic.org/articles/10.5334/ijic.6472: overlap: Close on loneliness requiring relational and community intervention, not better private interpretation alone.; difference: The candidate targets one spiritual-language pathway into real contact and repair.; novelty impact: Supports human-condition fit but reduces novelty of the intervention mechanism.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-contact-before-claim-cb3c919dd78ee510.md:63:- Internal Lumenary near-neighbors: Ask Who Taught The Answer, No Word Travels Alone, Stop When The Repair Changes, When Tools Become Judges, Not Every Check Should Be Yours, and Some Help Should Not Be Managed, supplied in project memory.: overlap: Extremely close on provenance gates, receiver wound, correction holder, anti-overchecking, and safety routing.; difference: This candidate sharpens one variable: public claim gets provenance first, stable private loneliness gets contact first.; novelty impact: Major local downgrade. Merge or cross-index unless blind readers can identify the routing variable without prompting.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-contact-before-claim-cb3c919dd78ee510.md:79:- If: Stable lonely seekers using borrowed spiritual sentences privately will benefit more from contact-first carry than from provenance-first auditing. Then: Over two and six weeks, a contact-first group shows lower loneliness and rumination, fewer identity-display posts, more real conversations, more help-seeking or repair actions, and no increase in shame compared with provenance-first and ordinary journaling arms. Weakens if: No improvement over ordinary journaling or social-support prompts, increased shame, increased rumination, or increased unsafe contact. Test surface: Four-arm randomized pilot: provenance-first gate, solo carry-first, contact-first carry-first, ordinary journaling plus social-support prompt.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-contact-before-claim-cb3c919dd78ee510.md:81:- If: Harmful borrowing is predicted more by substitution behavior than by borrowing itself. Then: Diary and social-media coding shows worse outcomes when borrowed sentences replace action, contact, correction, grief work, or help-seeking, even after controlling for whether the sentence is borrowed. Weakens if: Borrowing itself predicts harm independent of avoidance, identity display, public authority claims, source safety, and mental-health variables. Test surface: Longitudinal diary study with provenance coding, behavior coding, loneliness, rumination, help-seeking, correction, and real-contact measures.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-contact-before-claim-cb3c919dd78ee510.md:94:- clinicians familiar with OCD, scrupulosity, rumination, grief, loneliness, and depression
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-contact-before-claim-cb3c919dd78ee510.md:103:- What observable outcomes would convince you that the protocol helps loneliness rather than merely reducing posting, increasing compliance, or deepening dependence?
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-contact-before-claim-cb3c919dd78ee510.md:125:Novelty adjustment: Lower novelty from 0.50 to 0.46. The doctrine half is close to Panikkar, Freiberger, Smith, Sandmel, Lindbeck, Asad, and prior Lumenary translation-strain gates. The seeker half is close to Jamesian fruits, Ignatian discernment, Dogen practice-realization, Wuthnow's seeker spirituality, Turkle's conversation critique, social prescribing, behavioral activation, and anti-checking psychology. The contribution is a compact routing rule by function and wound. Human-condition fit is plausible but narrow: stable lonely or digitally unmoored seekers with meaning loss, feeling out of place, digital comparison, or achievement-contingent spiritual identity. Practice-testability drops sharply without a pre-contact safety screen and delayed provenance review.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-contact-before-claim-cb3c919dd78ee510.md:136:- Measure loneliness, rumination, shame, identity-display posts, real conversations, help-seeking, repair actions, unsafe-contact incidents, willingness to receive correction, and delayed provenance-review outcomes at two and six weeks.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-operational-remainder-ecology-39a96b7ef7849b21.json:83:      "overlap": "Close for the residue-policy component. The paper treats worldviews as risk factors, remedies, and meaning-making frames that shape the trajectory of meditation-related challenges.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-operational-remainder-ecology-39a96b7ef7849b21.json:142:    "answers_that_support_contribution": "Practitioners independently identify cases where the same self-negating instruction became safe or unsafe depending on the interaction of capacity, permitted meaning, and ecology, and they say the rubric would change screening, sequencing, or repair decisions.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-restating-is-not-realizing-1ed7e902d1f20ee6.json:43:      "test_surface": "Two-week pilot with WIP count, duplicate-output coding, action completion, rumination, shame, burnout, and novelty measures.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-restating-is-not-realizing-1ed7e902d1f20ee6.json:115:    "Pilot The Duplicate Check only with high-output overproducers and screen out severe depression, acute burnout, coercive workload, under-production, shame spirals, and cases where ordinary editorial revision is the real task."
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-restating-is-not-realizing-1ed7e902d1f20ee6.json:117:  "novelty_adjustment": "Lower novelty from 0.55 to 0.29. The live insight is a useful recursive application of an already logged Lumenary stopping rule. It should be merged with More Is Not The Same As Progress and The Answer You Keep Finding Is Already Settled. Human-condition fit is real but narrow: high-output researchers, writers, founders, students, and makers whose self-worth depends on continued production. It is not a fit for depressed under-producers, people in acute burnout who need rest, people under coercive workload, early exploratory phases without a real next action, or traditions where repetition is the practice itself.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-ask-who-taught-the-answer-53c355c0cbaee241.md:33:Risk of overread: Medium high. The regeneration gate may rename standard comparative method, homeomorphic equivalence, doctrine-as-grammar, source criticism, and teacherly discernment. It can also overcorrect into purity policing, as if borrowed language cannot become authentic through hybrid discipline. In direct-recognition or performative settings, the question what taught this sentence may itself be the wrong kind of check. Human-condition fit is plausible but narrow: stable eclectic adults and older teens dealing with digital comparison, meaning loss, loneliness, and feeling out of place. It is not for acute crisis, OCD or scrupulosity loops, dissociation, severe depression, mania, unsafe authority situations, or people under trusted guidance who should ask their teacher.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-ask-who-taught-the-answer-53c355c0cbaee241.md:55:- Internal Lumenary near-neighbors: No Word Travels Alone, A Shared Word Is Not Two Witnesses, Stop When The Repair Changes, and Translation Strain records, supplied in project memory.: overlap: Extremely close on source role, trained practice, correction holder, verification rule, provenance, bent meaning, dropped meaning, receiver wound, and counterfeit use.; difference: The candidate consolidates these into a regeneration gate and a Borrowed Sentence Check.; novelty impact: Major local downgrade. This should be cross-indexed or merged unless a blind distinct-content test shows separability.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-ask-who-taught-the-answer-53c355c0cbaee241.md:72:- If: Carrier fields are observable enough to code. Then: Independent coders can reach acceptable agreement on role, authority, verification, practice aim, what is bent, what is dropped, and what is added for narrow primary-text pairs. Weakens if: Coders cannot distinguish role from ontology, authority from verification, or bent meaning from dropped meaning above chance. Test surface: Inter-rater reliability study on Chandogya/SN 22.59, Dao De Jing/Pseudo-Dionysius, apophatic Buddhist/Christian pairs, and low-variance ritual instructions.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-ask-who-taught-the-answer-53c355c0cbaee241.md:95:- For digitally unmoored seekers, does this check reduce false belonging and identity display, or does it deepen shame, loneliness, and analysis paralysis?
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-ask-who-taught-the-answer-53c355c0cbaee241.md:117:Novelty adjustment: Lower novelty from 0.48 to 0.44. The theoretical core is close to Panikkar, Freiberger, Smith, Sandmel, Lindbeck, Asad, Sharf, Katz, source criticism, and recent Lumenary translation-strain records. The possible contribution is a compact regeneration gate that combines scholarly comparison with receiver safety and concrete action. Human-condition fit is clearer than for many abstract comparison records, but still bounded: it serves digital comparison, meaning loss, loneliness, and feeling out of place among stable eclectic readers. It is not a practice for acute distress, clinical checking loops, or guided practitioners who should use their actual teacher or care network.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-ask-who-taught-the-answer-53c355c0cbaee241.md:123:- Build a one-page codebook with fields for claim unit, source role, ontology, agency, practice aim, authority, correction holder, verification rule, provenance, bent meaning, dropped meaning, added meaning, receiver wound, concrete action, warning, repair, and clinical exclusion.
observations/claude/2026-05-29-you-cannot-release-what-you-never-held.md:22:- Prior-art audit: Michael A. Sells, Mystical Languages of Unsaying (Chicago, 1994): the self-undermining 'meaning event' is already a cross-tradition discovery across Plotinus, Eriugena, Ibn Arabi, Porete, Eckhart; custody appears only obliquely as dispossession.
observations/claude/2026-05-29-you-cannot-release-what-you-never-held.md:26:- Modern human-condition grounding: Curran and Hill (2019), Perfectionism Is Increasing Over Time, Psychological Bulletin 145(4): 410-429; corroborated by WHO burnout-as-occupational-phenomenon, Gallup State of the Global Workplace 2024, APA Stress in America 2024.
observations/claude/2026-05-29-you-cannot-release-what-you-never-held.md:56:Tags: method-release, achievement-pressure, burnout, cohort-fit, non-attachment
observations/claude/2026-05-29-you-cannot-release-what-you-never-held.md:72:Achievement-contingent self-worth and burnout, the habit of converting every result into a measure of personal value.
observations/claude/2026-05-29-you-cannot-release-what-you-never-held.md:104:Achievement-contingent self-worth and burnout among people who grip technique and convert outcomes into identity.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-silence-needs-a-second-voice-2c70888346a6050d.json:15:    "The target wound is loneliness and achievement-contingent self-worth in stable solo practitioners, not all contemplative silence."
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-silence-needs-a-second-voice-2c70888346a6050d.json:21:    "prediction": "High-perfectionism students, engineers, clinicians, or researchers who receive one bounded review plus one repair action will show less shame, less defensive interpretation, and faster useful action than those assigned solo meta-analysis of what the event says about them.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-silence-needs-a-second-voice-2c70888346a6050d.json:22:    "structural_translation": "When a person is prone to self-worth verdicts, asking them to classify the meaning of an ambiguous event can amplify the wound. A bounded second-person or rule-held review plus one concrete duty should reduce rumination.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-some-silence-needs-a-second-voice-2c70888346a6050d.json:37:      "test_surface": "Pilot stratified by reassurance seeking, intolerance of uncertainty, loneliness, and contingencies of self-worth.",
