reviews/originality/2026-05-30-first-ask-what-the-words-do-5bbc7c109ba18f80.md:100:Prediction: In psychoeducation for panic, dissociation-adjacent states, sleep paralysis, or burnout blankness, role labeling should reduce catastrophizing and identity conclusions more than content explanation alone.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stop-when-the-repair-changes-0e142612673940d0.md:12:A borrowed spiritual sentence is not ready to teach because its meaning seems to fit. It is ready only if the repair target, authority, verification, and ordinary-life action survive the crossing. If the repair changes, it must be named and tested as a new medicine.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stop-when-the-repair-changes-0e142612673940d0.md:32:Risk of overread: High. The model risks forcing traditions into modern therapeutic repair language. Pure Land nembutsu, Dzogchen pointing-out, sacramental speech, Dogen practice-realization, communal prayer, and ritual duty may function through vow, grace, recognition, participation, or formation rather than a named wound. Human-condition fit is real but narrow: stable unsupported seekers facing meaning loss, digital comparison, loneliness, and achievement-contingent certainty. It is not fit for acute crisis, dissociation, psychosis, mania, severe depression, OCD or scrupulosity loops, addiction withdrawal, unsafe authority, or medical blackout concerns.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stop-when-the-repair-changes-0e142612673940d0.md:50:- Wittgenstein language-games and forms of life, SEP, https://plato.stanford.edu/archives/fall2023/entries/wittgenstein/; Lindbeck cultural-linguistic doctrine, overview at https://readingreligion.org/9780664256040/the-nature-of-doctrine/: overlap: Very close on meaning depending on use, rules, and communal practice rather than isolated words.; difference: The candidate adds receiver wound, repair target, and ordinary-life test as a local gate.; novelty impact: Core language-travel premise is known.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stop-when-the-repair-changes-0e142612673940d0.md:114:Novelty adjustment: Lower novelty from 0.47 to 0.36. The useful contribution is a narrower repair-survival stopping rule for Lumenary publication, not a new theory of comparison or religious language. Human-condition fit is stronger than novelty, but only for stable supported seekers facing meaning loss, digital comparison, loneliness, and achievement-contingent spiritual certainty. Lower publishability if the cohort, non-fit cases, and safety stops are not explicit.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-stop-when-the-repair-changes-0e142612673940d0.md:119:- Build one codebook with fields for source sentence, source role, repair target, authority holder, verification rule, receiver wound, bent meaning, dropped meaning, added meaning, ordinary action, warning, repair, and clinical exclusion.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-translation-strain-as-a-load-test-for-convergence-7467567c4a12de58.md:62:- If: A strain rubric should change publication decisions compared with ordinary resemblance scoring. Then: Some high-similarity pairs should be downgraded because central meanings must be discarded, and some low-verbal-similarity pairs should be retained because functional role survives. Weakens if: The rubric produces the same decisions as ordinary expert judgment while adding only terminology. Test surface: Blind A/B comparison of 20 cross-tradition comparison records.
