./observations/codex/2026-05-30-stratified-post-negation-authorization.md:15:The candidate combines the proponent's residue-policy comparison with the challenger's vocabulary-bias critique and adds a stratum-level method. Neither original idea alone required every post-negation verdict to be coded by source layer, authorization mode, and practitioner effect. Its possible novelty is the claim that fidelity to tradition and usefulness to practitioners depend on the same discipline: do not let the frame decide what it claims to observe.
